Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:16.96,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:21.90,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.40,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:29.43,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
