Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:48.48,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:52.46,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
